{"tid":865663,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"TWICE成員真係相處得好融洽","createTime":"2018-10-17T08:45:05.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-19T09:20:38.000Z","uid":74065,"like":180,"dislike":16,"uniUserReply":51,"replies":[{"pid":"14b11f28385c5cc5fe4b808002a4efa138b10eac","tid":865663,"uid":74065,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-17T08:45:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Qai7GAE.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FQai7GAE.gif&h=3555d3b2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲Jungyeon和Sana（TWICE）爭吵的照片廣泛流傳<br />\n<br />\n兩位偶像站在MUSIC CORE的舞台上，似乎有點緊張感。 <br />\nSana以嚴肅的態度說話時，Jungyeon亦不停地大嗌著。<br />\n而 Momo發現後也悄悄地走開，去了其他地方。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/dccHvtW.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FdccHvtW.gif&h=209858b9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲Jungyeon最後的表情表示無語"},{"pid":"6b8d72f7a0f1d0b97de7089581f2d338ecd7ab44","tid":865663,"uid":213300,"like":268,"dislike":12,"score":256,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-17T08:47:42.000Z","msg":"尤其係娜璉<br />\n真係對子瑜同多賢好好<br />\n而且又靚女<br />\n娜璉係真女神<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9866a32fab2c342cca772c0e6b45aeb7cad8bedb","tid":865663,"uid":56701,"like":164,"dislike":0,"score":164,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-17T08:47:42.000Z","msg":"sana:你同我醒定啲呀！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"191eb7a8bb458d60c3909b426b95d12a8f93cbb5","tid":865663,"uid":60256,"like":33,"dislike":37,"score":-4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-17T08:48:19.000Z","msg":"成班西女人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 得賢B係善良"},{"pid":"0a4ad1938b04c6adf6a36f09b8b6ecfc1917f6de","tid":865663,"uid":63588,"like":78,"dislike":2,"score":76,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-17T08:49:07.000Z","msg":"往死𥚃打"},{"pid":"390ce63c168cf98a1e780721d8c06611e6ef0c6d","tid":865663,"uid":37146,"like":84,"dislike":63,"score":21,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-17T08:56:14.000Z","msg":"最尾咪笑返囉，做乜